name: Baby Pepe
additional_notices:
The following token has a variable tax function on the smart contract to change tax rates post deployment.
Do your own research and be careful if you are trading this token.

description.en:
What is Baby Pepe(Baby Pepe)?

Launched in 24/4/2023 by a Team based in United States of America, Baby Pepe is a meme-based cryptocurrency token operating on the BEP20 (Binance Smart Chain Blockchain). With great experience and knowledge within the core team, Baby Pepe will attempt to peak at the highest market cap possible for a Baby Pepe moon mission! Let’s bring back the old-school meme token days where everyone draws PEPE memes on the table.
